data.title: Heart Attack Killed Errol Flynn

data.text:
VANCOUVER, Friday

(A.A.P.-Reuter). —A coroner

ruled yesterday that Austra

lian-born actor Erroll Flynn

died from a heart attack—

and reported that a degener

ate liver contributed to his

death.

Coroner Glenn McDonald

said that there would be no

inquest on the actor who was

reported to have suffered

two previous heart attacks.
